{"tid":800994,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"印度教神話(一)--任意妄為的鬼父梵天(四面佛原型)","createTime":"2018-08-31T09:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T11:53:58.000Z","uid":204533,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"024614a40c43326f06db1dc1aa5d7263cc7dfe79","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">印度教神話(一)--任意妄為的鬼父梵天(四面佛原型)</div></strong></span><br />\n《喜馬拉亞星》是一套以印度教為背景的港產爛片。當中，印度教三主神之一的創世神梵天被描述成一直在發夢的純潔BB，並指世上「一切都係梵天的一場夢」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這只是一個相當誤導的和諧版本。因為梵天在印度教中形象負面，是一個相對不受崇拜，任意妄為的鬼父。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>印度教創世主</strong><br />\n首先，《喜馬拉亞星》當中提到的「一切都係梵天的一場夢」是相當有問題的。<br />\n<br />\n的確，梵天是印度教的創世主(毗濕奴派同濕婆派會不認同)。根據《梨俱吠陀》，在世界未存在前，在混沌之海上飄浮着一粒金蛋。突然，生主（現在被認為是梵天原型）把金蛋一分為二，破蛋而出。祂一站，舉高上方的蛋殼，化作天；祂一踩，把下方的蛋殼化作地。繼而，祂再慢慢創造方向、時間及各種元素。再之後，由於天地空三界都只得祂一個，祂覺得空虛覺得寂寞覺得凍，心想：「不如整班仆街出黎比我玩吓！」於是，祂便便開始<del>玩模擬人生，</del>著手創造世間萬物，包括天神、人、魔等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/4/3149/2883154338_05566eaa9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F4%2F3149%2F2883154338_05566eaa9c.jpg&h=53d796fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是，梵天並非在發夢時創作世界。相反，祂是在醒着時創造世界，當祂訓着，世界就走到終結。原因是梵天一天之開始等於世界開始，梵天一天的完結代表世界毀滅。根據《薄伽梵往世書》，人的一年等於天神的一天。天神的一千年稱作爭鬥時代，二千年稱作二分時代，三千年稱作三分時代，四千年稱作圓滿時代，而四個時代的總和的一千二百倍稱作一個<del>少女時代</del>天神時代。而二千個天神時代才等於梵天的一天，而梵天的一天正是世界由開始走到終結。<br />\n<img src=\"https://gpstatic.com/acache/23/76/1/uk/s1-667139bb400e6233b7788b132364c279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgpstatic.com%2Facache%2F23%2F76%2F1%2Fuk%2Fs1-667139bb400e6233b7788b132364c279.jpg&h=4a9e435f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"220e5a912ad73d9cdd6727e098ece01a0fbea174","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>鬼父ｘ四面佛</strong><br />\n作為一個創世主，理應會像其他宗教的創世主受尊崇，但在現今印度眾多寺廟當中，卻只有少數是祭祀祂（相反，在泰國卻受崇拜，成為四面佛）。印度大多寺廟多是崇拜三主神中的其餘兩位：濕婆和毗濕奴。原因是自往世書時期開始，有着眾多不利於祂的神話情節。<br />\n<br />\n其中一則是關於祂的四面佛來源。話說，有一天，祂左手手指公生出了美麗非凡的辯才天女。辯才天女有多美呢?根據神話及神像，辯才天女皮膚白皙，永遠青春，而且有前有後，雅利安人種的美人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KBcgUTS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKBcgUTS.jpg&h=c45e9364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梵天一望就流晒口水，不能自拔地視姦着辯才天女。<br />\n<br />\n辯才天女感受到梵天灼熱的視線，心想：「死變態佬！」。於是，她轉到梵天的前後左右，甚至飛到梵天頭上去迴避。<br />\n<br />\n梵天作為創世神級的痴漢，當然有應對方法。那就是在本身的頭顱之外，額外生出四個頭，總共五個方位（前後左右上）全天候地視姦辯才天女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vb60ovj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVb60ovj.jpg&h=1a61819f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n辯才天女深怕梵天會有進一步行動，便求助於三主神中的毀滅神濕婆。濕婆忍受不了梵天的鬼父行徑，便砍下了梵天的一個頭。於<span style=\"color: red;\">是，梵天便餘下四個頭。其後梵天神傳到東南亞其他地方，如泰國，便成四面佛。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KfsdMOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKfsdMOF.jpg&h=0cd41b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n濕婆因為砍下了創世神的一個頭，而引起其他天神對他不滿，包括梵天兒子、濕婆的未來外父達剎，為未來的濕婆的悲劇埋下了種子。<br />\n<br />\n而辯才天女亦因此短暫地避開了父女相姦的情節。但是，這只是短暫地避開。因為她其後嫁了給三主神中的保護神毗濕奴，做祂的第三個老婆。正所謂三個女人一個墟，毗濕奴嫌她們太嘈太煩，便把其中一個老婆送給濕婆，<span style=\"color: red;\">把辯才天女送給梵天，只留下一個老婆給自己。<br />\n<br />\n所以，最後梵天還是如願以償，成為了鬼父。</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iZ0AVJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiZ0AVJO.jpg&h=8e9e3ee8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"230e6f5edd33c7a0f98b94bbff5e8e8b6d61c0c5","tid":800994,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n雅利安人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c207b8c1187f870ed1dc18077e27e9f1bf282","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>走數的主神</strong><br />\n另一則令梵天形象負面的神話情節是祂走數。話說有次，梵天與毗濕奴在爭論誰才更加偉光正。<br />\n<br />\n「我比你更偉大更光榮更正確！」<br />\n「收皮啦你！你連自己個女都搞，你敢話自己正確？唔怕笑死人？」<br />\n「你當老婆係舊衫，周街派，唔通你又好我好多？」<br />\n<br />\n突然，濕婆的林伽（巨撚）憑空出現貫穿天地空三界，而遠處傳來濕婆的聲音：「拗咩吖你兩條友，我先係真正偉大，睇野啦！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1Z_UCdoJCh4/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1Z_UCdoJCh4%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=1bd8e81a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看見林伽後，兩位主神「嘩」了一聲，之後望一望自己下身，然後又望一望對方，不服氣地說：「唓！好大咩？我地搵唔到盡頭既話先叫偉大！」<br />\n<br />\n之後，毗濕奴便作野豬，向下找了一千年；梵天就化作天鵝向上飛了一千年。兩者也找不到林伽的盡頭，但又開始疲累，於是便回出發地。此時濕婆出現。毗濕奴便認輸。<br />\n<br />\n但梵天不認輸，並且用法力令露兜樹花替他說謊，說祂已見到盡頭：「嗱！你聽到啦！我搵得到盡頭，你條鳩都唔算好大姐。唔可以叫偉大！最偉大都係我呢個創世神！」<br />\n<br />\n濕婆聽後，便握緊拳頭：「屌你老母！你條死仆街做神都講大話，以後一定唔受信眾崇拜！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/79/Youidiot.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110608015448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F79%2FYouidiot.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110608015448&h=9bd842f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自始梵天便受詛咒，不受信眾崇拜。現今印度只有一間神廟敬拜他。"},{"pid":"7da6adc12099c6e9ce44d3b3604d00b732b59c91","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>結語</strong><br />\n除了上述兩個故事外，另外還有許多則令梵天形象負面的情節，例如祂多次賜予不同的阿修羅王「只有ＸＸ才能殺死你」之類的無雙神力，使得天神多次被阿修羅打敗、驅逐，令天下大亂，但就不負責，要毗濕奴及濕婆等幫祂執屎（有機會之後再介紹）。<br />\n<br />\n總括而言，梵天雖然是創世神，但卻形象負面，令祂在現今印度本土卻不太受尊崇。"},{"pid":"121baa5aa7f4d50df5f8767fce6c5d9893fea056","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>後記</strong>：梵天形象負面，只限往世書時代至現今，在吠陀經時代，祂是備受尊重的。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有人會問為何會產生相關的神話，踩低梵天？原因是政治角力，簡單來說是歷史長河中，代表不同種姓的宗教及教內教派政治角力的結果。有機會再分析。"},{"pid":"0d38b170288b56e489a88e7294a71d48da20534a","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"小弟其他文章: <br />\n<strong>耶教史（上）由多神教演變成一神教</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n漢傳佛教的陰暗面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4423bad8b44f5c76036e4de5afabc8f93b067996","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2muIJGdCTMg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2muIJGdCTMg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6d7607b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辯才天女<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s11.sinaimg.cn/middle/8b856980gb78f5f1e42aa&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs11.sinaimg.cn%2Fmiddle%2F8b856980gb78f5f1e42aa%26690&h=4a16d7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被佛教吸納後的辯才天"},{"pid":"f3468402c9f2edc512f9c0944b0e61862e480848","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://religion.moi.gov.tw/WebCtrl/FileStore/CKUpload/206%E6%A2%B5%E5%A4%A9-1%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E9%A6%AC%E8%8F%9F%E7%BE%85%EF%BC%88Mathur%C4%81%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%90%B3%E5%BE%B7%E6%9C%97%E6%94%9D%EF%BC%89%20DSC_0204.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Freligion.moi.gov.tw%2FWebCtrl%2FFileStore%2FCKUpload%2F206%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E5%25A4%25A9-1%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%258F%259F%25E7%25BE%2585%25EF%25BC%2588Mathur%25C4%2581%25EF%25BC%2589%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BB%259F%25EF%25BC%2588%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2594%259D%25EF%25BC%2589%2520DSC_0204.JPG&h=9b151759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梵天<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTq7g5Y_n-oVpTcgXT6f4Og_6By-qdsR1vhQQTz5hvc09EbnrbF6g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTq7g5Y_n-oVpTcgXT6f4Og_6By-qdsR1vhQQTz5hvc09EbnrbF6g&h=c557a6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被佛教吸納後的梵天（四面佛）"},{"pid":"4b6cb2d61d084e91f89d8a0ca3dcb68c9558ea33","tid":800994,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"等密特拉出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174e4c137acadcc99d29047bf81abc7168c9eacc","tid":800994,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3468402c9f2edc512f9c0944b0e61862e480848","tid":800994,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://religion.moi.gov.tw/WebCtrl/FileStore/CKUpload/206%E6%A2%B5%E5%A4%A9-1%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E9%A6%AC%E8%8F%9F%E7%BE%85%EF%BC%88Mathur%C4%81%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%90%B3%E5%BE%B7%E6%9C%97%E6%94%9D%EF%BC%89%20DSC_0204.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Freligion.moi.gov.tw%2FWebCtrl%2FFileStore%2FCKUpload%2F206%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E5%25A4%25A9-1%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%258F%259F%25E7%25BE%2585%25EF%25BC%2588Mathur%25C4%2581%25EF%25BC%2589%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BB%259F%25EF%25BC%2588%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2594%259D%25EF%25BC%2589%2520DSC_0204.JPG&h=9b151759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梵天<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTq7g5Y_n-oVpTcgXT6f4Og_6By-qdsR1vhQQTz5hvc09EbnrbF6g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTq7g5Y_n-oVpTcgXT6f4Og_6By-qdsR1vhQQTz5hvc09EbnrbF6g&h=c557a6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被佛教吸納後的梵天（四面佛）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"四面佛唔係佛教，佛教冇人會拜梵天"},{"pid":"70a4011dd5f4f94bee500522371e7b1a198aeab0","tid":800994,"uid":107656,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:58:48.000Z